sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Ledger as Archive-Ledger
  participant OS as ArchiveOS
  participant Policy as Policy Evidence
  participant PM as PM / Admin
  participant Callback as Callback Outbox

  Ledger->>Ledger: Detect APPROVAL_REQUIRED transaction
  Ledger->>OS: POST external approval request
  OS->>Policy: Build RAG evidence
  alt LLM or RAG unavailable
    Policy-->>OS: Rule fallback evidence
  else Evidence available
    Policy-->>OS: Policy evidence snapshot
  end
  OS->>PM: Show approval request
  PM->>OS: Approve / reject / hold
  OS->>Callback: Store callback outbox item
  Callback->>Ledger: POST approval callback
  Ledger->>Ledger: Update transaction status
  Ledger-->>OS: Callback accepted
  OS->>OS: Audit decision and callback result

